      "severity": "high",
      "description": "Eight output types (assessment, quiz, rubric, formative_check, warm_up, vocabulary_card, observation_grid, lesson_reflection) have router keys and renderer family mappings but no HTML template and are not in DOC_OUTPUT_TYPES. render-package.mjs logs 'Skipping unsupported doc-mode route' and continues without failing. A package declaring these types appears to render successfully but produces no artifact.",
