      "description": "lesson_overview and checkpoint_sheet are in DOC_OUTPUT_TYPES (so they attempt Python rendering) but have no dedicated render function in engine/pdf/render_stable_core_output.py. They may fall through to a generic base renderer or silently produce nothing.",
